These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: emerald, green, pink, lilac, ivory, coral
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, epic, superhero, western, zombie
 1. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 2. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 3. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is between the person who likes ivory and the person watching disaster movies##2
 5. the person watching western movies is the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes green##1
 8. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
 9. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
11. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4    |    5     |  6   |
| Color      | pink | lilac   | ivory | emerald | green    | coral  |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | superhero | zombie   | crime  | disaster | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, collecting, filmmaking, hiking, video-games, woodworking
6 different games are played: chess, monopoly, snooker, bridge, whist, poker
 1. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
11. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
12. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person playing chess##1
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
15. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
16. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | filmmaking | chess         | collecting | hiking |
| Game   | chess    | whist      | snooker      | bridge | monopoly   | poker |

