.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea
The people have 6 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, chef, engineer, doctor, writer
 1. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the engineer##1
 4. the musician is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 7. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 9. the chef is on the left or right of the writer##3
10. the writer is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
12. the security-guard is on the right of the chef##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | cola     | fanta  | tea     | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |
| Job       | musician | writer | chef | security-guard | engineer          | doctor   |

