 1. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
13. the person drinking juice is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | mirinda   | coffee    | water    | iced-tea |
| Pet   | pony   | rabbit | dog | snake | goat | rat |

