 4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 5. the person driving the train is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
10. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
11. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | water  | tea        | sprite  | fanta     | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Transport       | tram | train | bike | snowmobile | quad-bike  | bus          |

