.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: traveling, photography, cooking, card-games, sudoku, camping
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bus, car, motorbike, subway, taxi
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Hobby         | camping    | card-games | photography   | cooking | traveling    | sudoku |
| Transport   | airplane | taxi  | subway | car      | motorbike | bus    |

 